               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">JOHN OLIVER GRAY</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18620106-184-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18620106-184-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18620106-184-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There were five other indictments against the prisoners, upon which no evidence was offered.</hi>
